Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:44.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 3 months since the battle \Nwith the Skrugg was finished. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:51.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace has returned to the city, but it's not \Nlike everything is the way it used to be. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:59.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep scars remain from the Skrugg, and a \Nlarge number of people lost their homes. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:05.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those spheres stopped moving, and \Nhave remained where they are. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:09.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like we have the technology \Non this planet to reactivate them. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:14.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard on the news that the government
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:20.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,has finished surrounding the sphere in front \Nof the White House with a research lab. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:26.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The utilities and transportation networks \Nhaven't been fully restored yet, either. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:31.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Even so... 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, just hold it like that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! No problem! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:36.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:37.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, set... 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:44.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the city is taking \Na new step toward tomorrow. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:48.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've got a ton more work \Nto do at my part-time job! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:53.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey! I've got a lot of \Nwork again for you today! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Thank you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the latest reports,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:08.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the reconstruction of the areas destroyed \Nby the spheres is proceeding as scheduled. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:12.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what of the investigation into the Skrugg? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:17.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, Sir, but although we \Nare investigating quite diligently,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:22.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we still know nothing of the codenamed \N"Ghost" that destroyed the Skrugg. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:24.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, no change on that front. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:30.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there have been small incidents \Nin Center City during its reconstruction. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:31.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidents? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:35.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I would hesitate to \Neven call them that.... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:39.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Overnight, piles of rubble have been cleaned up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:42.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,ground has been leveled,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:45.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,scaffolding has been erected... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:49.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like someone is assisting \Nwith the rebuilding of the city. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The work always seems to \Noccur over a single night. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:57.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And these are jobs that would take many \Nweeks to finish even using heavy equipment. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that this "Mr. \NHero" is hiding out in that city? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:11.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no guarantee that this \Nhero will always be on our side. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:18.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, if this mysterious hero \Nand the Ghost are one in the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:22.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the United States cannot \Nturn a blind eye to them. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some evidence? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:34.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a printout from a \Nsecurity camera in the city. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:41.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This Ghost may became a threat \Nto the United States. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Hughes. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:53.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him handle this. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:05.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, out of the way! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:11.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You pitiful ants! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:25.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is inadvisable to become \Noverly emotional, Dr. Minami. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:26.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, damn it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:33.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do {\i1}I{\i0} have to help out here in Center City? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:37.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly because the Skrugg were destroyed \Nprior to you stopping the sphere. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, damn it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:47.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, my beautiful work of art is \Nbeing put to work rebuilding this puny city! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:51.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some other reason \Nfor involving the MR-1? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course there is! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:56.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't stand even watching it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then perhaps you should not watch it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:00.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:04.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You expect me to leave my work \Nof art in other people's hands? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should watch it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's in this city somewhere... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:15.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that got in the way \Nof my grand ambition... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:18.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in this city! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:23.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Joey?  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:25.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not getting enough sleep? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yeah... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:28.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:39.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going to go, Will? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:46.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't stay here any longer. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:51.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't live in human society with this body. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer be with you, Lina. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:55.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay strong, Lina. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:17.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen him since. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:24.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother said he's sure to return. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:29.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And my dad seems to be \Ntrying to forget about him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:31.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,by absorbing himself in \Nthe reconstruction work. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:48.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:50.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, good morning. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Okay, I guess. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:03.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:07.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Lina... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a lot happened and all...  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But keep on working hard! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If something's up, tell me anything. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be happy to lend an ear. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:20.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something I can handle. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:26.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just talking about things can \Nmake people feel better, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Thanks. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:38.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, um... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:44.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...go out on a date... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you go out with... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, Lina! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:58.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem? You'd better \Nhurry or class will start. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta run! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:16.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Using this distributive law,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:20.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you can take these products of polynomials\Nand turn them into a single polynomial. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:23.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called the polynomial expansion. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:28.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is the opposite process from factorization,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:29.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When class is over, I'll \Nask him out, no excuses! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:34.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}which we studied previously, therefore you \Ncan use that process to check your work. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:33.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ask him nice and quick before anyone \Ninterrupts, then it should go fine. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:39.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all for today. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lina... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you see... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:46.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:50.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey Jones! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you come here for a bit? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:02.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:17.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried making it yesterday. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:24.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on here! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:34.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling like I heard Lina's voice. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be your imagination. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:48.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna ask him out, this time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:50.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if something gets in my way, I don't care. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to get him to promise, then... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lina. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I want to talk about something. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:02.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just take a second. Do you mind? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:04.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Am I in the way? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You are. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just be quiet! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:11.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine, I get it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Joey. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Three thirty. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:25.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Lina! I have to \Nhurry to my part-time job! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:28.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll run with you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:31.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running with you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:34.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's go. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:43.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Dad? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:45.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:48.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, really? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:50.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm in a hurry. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:54.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't talking to you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:04.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:27.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you get me another cup of coffee? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you fill me up as well? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:34.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, of course. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:37.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:38.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:46.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad. The coffee here is top notch. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Best instant coffee you can buy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:50.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:52.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't taste the difference, \Nget outta my store. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry... Fill 'er up. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you also here to help with the reconstruction? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:02.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, something like that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:07.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The city needs a lot of workers to help \Nwith the rebuilding and construction. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:10.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to that, I've got a lot more work. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Good for you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:13.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:14.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, uh... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, Joey. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:20.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard the rumors? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:21.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What rumors? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:24.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That there's some hero that shows up
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:28.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and helps with the reconstruction in \Nthe middle of night, uncalled for. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:37.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe it's just some urban legend. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're investigating those rumors? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:46.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Just wondering what you \Nthought of someone that kind. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's the work of God. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:50.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a giant help. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:53.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? I \Nwon't have any work left to do! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:00.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should cut back \Non anything too flashy... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:10.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then ready... Start! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... Go! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:41.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:44.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:48.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:58.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, what's this? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:04.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman's power comes from electricity. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:10.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Electricity is the origin of magnetism, and \Nhas the power to attract and repel things. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:16.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you two have improved \Nconsiderably these past three months. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:19.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus your teamwork has \Nmade remarkable progress. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some new attacks, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, since the Skrugg are \Ngone, why am I doing this? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:31.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? The Skrugg aren't \Nthe only threat to the world, you know. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:37.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious that you must make all \Npossible preparations for the next time. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:41.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Studying construction is \Nmore useful to the city... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:46.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how to pour concrete, or how to \Nerect a steel frame foundation... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:59.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey. You're the only one who can use Heroman. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:03.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do it, who will? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:15.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see Heroman \Nlike that ever again... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:20.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:22.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, and that's that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Professor Denton... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:28.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:32.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there are rumors about \NHeroman at my part-time job earlier. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:35.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about the volunteer work \Nyou're doing at night? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:36.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:44.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the rumors I've heard are that there are \Ngovernment types going around investigating. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:50.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's ever going to think that your \Ntoy is some hero of justice or anything. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:56.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That being said, I recommend that you \Ntake all precaution in your actions. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make up your mind. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:46.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:52.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, hello? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.78,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey! It's Joey, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about today. My job... 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.18,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where are you right now? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:08.01,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I- 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:11.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina? Lina? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:12.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina... 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:20.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:37.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was... 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet down, you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this, little princess. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:47.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay quiet and we won't \Nhave to get our hands dirty. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:50.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For a little while, anyway... 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to hate someone, hate your dad! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:58.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We realized he must have been crazy rich after\Nhe started doin' all that flashy charity work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:02.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious his daughter \Nwould be targeted, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:08.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as your dad coughs up\Nthe cash we'll go easy on you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep quiet until then. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:30.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a strange one here... 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:31.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move outta the way! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring me? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Boss... 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a monster! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stay back! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:07.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina... Lina! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey... 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared... 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:41.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I knew you would come for me... 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:53.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Here is fine. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:55.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll be going. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for today. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Lina. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to ask him out on a date! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:24.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I say it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:26.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a simple thing... 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:33.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to go out somewhere \Ntogether on Sunday, Joey? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:39.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... You forgot... 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:45.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how we finally \Npromised to go out on a date! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:49.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did we do? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the victims! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were attacked by a monster! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:56.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't do anything wrong! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:58.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We got you on illegal possession \Nof firearms, at least! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:21:59.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those aren't ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a break! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:07.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Special Agent Hughes. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:11.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting to the President. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:15.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ghost... is real. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:24.09,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"Can you hear this voice?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:31.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been calling that, always, from deep within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:45.46,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you, all alone, let another lonely one be next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:51.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because together it's not lonely, it's twoly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:56.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you're not alone any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:22:59.99,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because there's no one next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:02.54,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't mean that I'm lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:07.74,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone to notice this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:13.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,that heart must have surely cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:16.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we'll crush to bits
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.65,0:23:20.35,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the fortress of our limitless sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:24.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:27.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? I'm running through at full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:31.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,To where you're waiting, left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:34.64,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,in the place of tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:39.77,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you, with burning passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:43.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:52.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Heroman: 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.63,0:23:55.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is everyone out there most afraid of? 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:57.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For me... For me... 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.30,0:24:01.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hughes's investigation is \Ngetting closer to the truth,  
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:05.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but Joey has bigger problems than that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:11.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the entrance of, in Joey's view, the \Ngreatest evil of all, Joey shudders and weeps in fear! 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.35,0:24:15.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Heroman #11: Menace. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:18.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... Attack! 
